line_1: The rav'nous Eagle, and the noisy Mew
line_2: Fearless thro' Waves the scaly Prey pursue.

line_1: Which when observ'd, he shrunk into his Mew,
line_2: And shone all glittering with ungodly Dew,

line_1: Which when observ'd, he shrunk into his Mew,
line_2: And strait would recollect his Piety anew.
